      • EllipticalOrbitAnimation3D

        public EllipticalOrbitAnimation3D(Vector3 focalPoint,
                          Vector3 periapsis,
                          Vector3 normal,
                          double eccentricity,
                          EllipticalOrbitAnimation3D.OrbitDirection direction)
        Defines an elliptical orbit around a point.
        Parameters:
        focalPoint - Point which the ATransformable3D orbits around.
        periapsis - Point which the object passes closest to the focal point.
        normal - Normal to the orbital plane. This defines the orbital inclination.
        eccentricity - Eccentricity of the orbit. Zero value results in a circular orbit.
        direction - Direction of the orbit.
